 (10001,'asvperumal@imail.com','asvperumal@imail.com','As a close-knit team of software engineers, designers, and developers, our combined  experience and skill set make us a well-equipped team to develop entirely new software  solutions or advise on the ideal IT system for your business.  Challenges are our greatest opportunity to do great work, so if there is  a special project you have in mind please speak to our offices in greater detail for a bespoke  quote.  We look forward to working with you.   As discussed, App Development is done from our end. Requirement regarding this project is  mentioned below:','As a close-knit team of software engineers, designers, and developers, our combined \r\nexperience and skill set make us a well-equipped team to develop entirely new software \r\nsolutions or advise on the ideal IT system for your business. \r\nChallenges are our greatest opportunity to do great work, so if there is \r\na special project you have in mind please speak to our offices in greater detail for a bespoke \r\nquote. \r\nWe look forward to working with you.  \r\nAs discussed, App Development is done from our end. Requirement regarding this project is \r\nmentioned below:','2-12-2025','03:13:48 PM','spams','%PDF-1.5\r%Ã¢Ã£ÃÃ\r\n1 0 obj\n<</Metadata 2 0 R/Outlines 5 0 R/Pages 3 0 R/SaveStreams<</Q 6 0 R/q 7 0 R>>/Type/Catalog>>\nendobj\n2 0 obj\n<</Length 3742/Subtype/XML/Type/Metadata>>stream\r\n<?xpacket begin=\"Ã¯Â»Â¿\" id=\"W5M0MpCehiHzreSzNTczkc9d\"?>\n<x:xmpmeta xmlns:x=\"adobe:ns:meta/\" x:xmptk=\"Adobe XMP Core 5.2-c001 63.143651, 2012/04/05-09:01:49        \">\n   <rdf:RDF xmlns:rdf=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#\">\n      <rdf:Description rdf:about=\"\"\n            xmlns:xmp=\"http://ns.adobe.com/xap/1.0/\">\n         <xmp:ModifyDate>2020-01-27T15:17:02-05:00</xmp:ModifyDate>\n         <xmp:CreateDate>2020-01-27T15:17:01-05:00</xmp:CreateDate>\n         <xmp:MetadataDate>2020-01-27T15:17:02-05:00</xmp:MetadataDate>\n         <x